{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_520.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, about that thing before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Thing? Oh, do you mean...that thing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yup, the \"let's exact vengeance upon Juris\" strategy... It's not working out so well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "On that note, this is what Juris really can't stand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "This is...really spicy, right?<CR>Juris doesn't like spicy food?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Correctamundo. He's like a kid, right? So my plan was to sneak this into his food, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "As spicy as it is, this has just as strong of a smell, so he'll know right away that it's in his dish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Exactly! Plus, the food turns bright red, too, so he'll figure it out right away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "So, this is where I need your help. Can you make an odorless, colorless food that's just as spicy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I heard from Ernie that you're really good at this sort of thing, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't think I'm particularly good at it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Plus, it could be possible for me to make it, but I'd feel bad for Juris..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "You shouldn't be. I'm only doing this for his sake, since he's gotten so carried away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'm trying to teach him that you shouldn't do things to people that you know they won't like."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "This isn't just a prank!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I-If you say so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Please! I'm begging you! It's not like I'm going to use it for evil!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Umm, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "And your reward will be free<CR>all-you-can-eat lunches for a year!<CR>How does that sound!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Urgh...that's very tempting..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I'll even include the added bonus of one free dessert with your meal. See? Don't you wanna do this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...okay, I'll do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "*gasp* I answered that subconsciously! Mix Master, I didn't mean it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, it's too late now. You already said yes, so it's a deal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Bring it to me once it's done. I'll be looking forward to it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "(I-I feel like I made a terrible<CR>promise...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You learned how to make Hell Soup."
        }
    ]
}